item.title: Main Information
item.description: There is nothing here yet, but it probably will. What will it be? Something insignificant, like ourselves, but interesting for me. This site is proof that bad qualities have positive sides. It came about because I stole an idea from a very talented friend of mine (it’s true). If you can see this, thank you) What will be specific here will be written in “about”. But, in short, small handicraft projects and sad but attractive stories.

item.description: Приезжаем вечно поздно: “Здравствуй, ночь. Привет, кровать”. Мы мечтаем в ней о звездах, В потолок смотря опять
